column1: If user knowledge not equal to 2 OR ( user income greater than or equal to 3143 AND user marital status not equal to yes ) , then 5.
If user gender equal to female , then not 2.
If user income lesser than 7941 OR user gender not equal to male , then 1.
If user marital status not equal to no OR user knowledge equal to 5 , then not 3.
